  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "1a2b3c4d-5e6f-7a8b-9c0d-1e2f3a4b5c6d",
    "name": "Employee Onboarding MCP Services - Complete with NLP Integration",
    "description": "🤖 **COMPREHENSIVE COLLECTION: MCP Services + Agent Broker + NLP Integration**\n\n## 🚀 Services Covered:\n\n### 1. **Agent Broker MCP** - Central Orchestrator\n- **Base URL**: https://employee-onboarding-agent-broker.us-e1.cloudhub.io/api\n- **Purpose**: Central orchestration hub with advanced NLP processing\n- **Features**: Complete workflow orchestration, NLP-powered conversation management\n\n### 2. **Employee Onboarding MCP** - Employee Lifecycle\n- **Base URL**: https://employee-onboarding-mcp-server.us-e1.cloudhub.io/api\n- **Purpose**: Employee profile management and HR processes\n- **Features**: CRUD operations, status tracking, onboarding workflows\n\n### 3. **Asset Allocation MCP** - IT Asset Management\n- **Base URL**: https://assets-allocation-mcp-server.us-e1.cloudhub.io/api\n- **Purpose**: Smart asset allocation and inventory management\n- **Features**: Asset tracking, availability checking, automated allocation\n\n### 4. **Email Notification MCP** - Communication Hub\n- **Base URL**: https://email-notification-mcp-server.us-e1.cloudhub.io/api\n- **Purpose**: Multi-channel notification delivery\n- **Features**: Email templates, delivery tracking, personalization\n\n### 5. **🧠 NLP & Agent Fabric Integration** - AI-Powered Interface\n- **React Client**: Intelligent conversation processing\n- **Purpose**: Natural language processing with MCP orchestration\n- **Features**: Intent recognition, entity extraction, contextual responses\n\n## 🌟 New Features in this Collection:\n\n✨ **NLP-Powered Interactions**: Test natural language queries that get processed into MCP actions\n✨ **Agent Fabric Orchestration**: Advanced AI-driven workflow coordination\n✨ **Conversation Management**: Multi-turn dialog support with context awareness\n✨ **Sentiment Analysis**: Emotion-aware response generation\n✨ **Predictive Insights**: AI recommendations based on interaction patterns\n✨ **Multi-Modal Testing**: Support for various input types and response formats\n\n## 📊 Test Scenarios Included:\n\n🔹 **Individual MCP Service Testing**: Each service tested independently\n🔹 **End-to-End Workflow Testing**: Complete onboarding processes\n🔹 **NLP Integration Testing**: Natural language to MCP action conversion\n🔹 **Agent Fabric Intelligence**: Advanced AI orchestration scenarios\n🔹 **Error Handling & Recovery**: Comprehensive error scenario testing\n🔹 **Performance & Load Testing**: Service reliability validation\n\n## 🔧 Environment Variables:\n- `agent_broker_url`: employee-onboarding-agent-broker.us-e1.cloudhub.io\n- `employee_onboarding_url`: employee-onboarding-mcp-server.us-e1.cloudhub.io\n- `asset_allocation_url`: assets-allocation-mcp-server.us-e1.cloudhub.io\n- `notification_url`: email-notification-mcp-server.us-e1.cloudhub.io\n- `react_client_url`: localhost:3000 (for NLP testing)\n\n**Version**: 3.0.0 - Enhanced with NLP & Agent Fabric\n**Updated**: 2024-03-04\n**Compatibility**: CloudHub 2.0, Mule 4.9+, React Client NLP Integration",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "46229874"
  },
