            "description": "📊 **Natural Language Status Inquiry**\n\nAllows conversational status checking with comprehensive analytics.\n\n**Intelligence Features:**\n- Employee identification from context\n- Progress analysis\n- Timeline predictions\n- Risk assessment\n- Bottleneck identification\n\n**Example Queries:**\n- \"How is John's onboarding going?\"\n- \"Check progress for the new Marketing hire\"\n- \"Is Emily ready to start work?\""
          },
